hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 单周期演化算符为
$$
U(T,0)=e^{-\frac{i}{\hbar}H_A\,\frac{T}{4}}\;
e^{-\frac{i}{\hbar}H_B\,\frac{T}{2}}\;
e^{-\frac{i}{\hbar}H_A\,\frac{T}{4}}.
$$
2. 代入 $H_A=\epsilon\sigma_z$，$H_B=\Delta\sigma_x$，并定义
$$
\alpha=\frac{\epsilon T}{4\hbar}, 
\quad
\beta=\frac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}.
$$
则
$$
e^{-\frac{i}{\hbar}H_A\,\frac{T}{4}}
=e^{-i\alpha\sigma_z}
=\begin{pmatrix}e^{-i\alpha}  0\\0  e^{i\alpha}\end{pmatrix},
\quad
e^{-\frac{i}{\hbar}H_B\,\frac{T}{2}}
=e^{-i\beta\sigma_x}
=\cos\beta\,I - i\sin\beta\,\sigma_x
=\begin{pmatrix}\cos\beta  -i\sin\beta\\-i\sin\beta  \cos\beta\end{pmatrix}.
$$
3. 分两步计算乘积：
$$
M_1=e^{-i\alpha\sigma_z}\,e^{-i\beta\sigma_x}
=\begin{pmatrix}
e^{-i\alpha}\cos\beta   -i e^{-i\alpha}\sin\beta\\
-i e^{i\alpha}\sin\beta   e^{i\alpha}\cos\beta
\end{pmatrix},
$$
$$
U(T,0)=M_1\,e^{-i\alpha\sigma_z}
=\begin{pmatrix}
e^{-i\alpha}\cos\beta e^{-i\alpha}  -i e^{-i\alpha}\sin\beta e^{i\alpha}\\
-i e^{i\alpha}\sin\beta e^{-i\alpha}  e^{i\alpha}\cos\beta e^{i\alpha}
\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}
\cos\beta e^{-2i\alpha}  -i\sin\beta\\
-i\sin\beta  \cos\beta e^{2i\alpha}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$
4. 回到原始参数 $2\alpha=\frac{\epsilon T}{2\hbar}$，$\beta=\frac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}$，得到
$$
U(T,0)
=\begin{pmatrix}
\cos\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)e^{-i\frac{\epsilon T}{2\hbar}}
  -i\sin\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)\\
-i\sin\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)
  \cos\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)e^{i\frac{\epsilon T}{2\hbar}}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$

hands_on_practices.answer:
$$
\boxed{
\begin{pmatrix}
\cos\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)e^{-i\frac{\epsilon T}{2\hbar}}
  -i\sin\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)\\
-i\sin\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)
  \cos\bigl(\tfrac{\Delta T}{2\hbar}\bigr)e^{i\frac{\epsilon T}{2\hbar}}
\end{pmatrix}
}
$$
